  Locus:
    Page: 443
    Verse: 8
Tags:
  - Speech
---
Keep your remarks brief, otherwise the complete plan of your thoughts will
seldom be grasped. Before you reach the conclusion, the listener will have
forgotten the beginning and the middle.
